resources.string: FIRST FRC Team 2169 KING TeC is a robotics team based out of Prior Lake High School in Savage, MN. This app was developed as a resource to other FIRST FRC teams and as a way to help these teams succeed. For more information, or to find out how you can help support KING TeC, please email us at apps@kingtec2169.com. App development was led by Ryan Z. and Mason T., with content provided by Haley S., Michael R. and Andrew K.
